  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I wrote-- I wrote a summary of the play, and I finished up somewhat by saying that, yes, and I would like to [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] sink my sword into the heart of that awful-- I think it was a Czech person displayed in this-- in this play.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I won the award, right, because I have-- I have-- you know, it was such a-- such a good summary of the play.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Which was, again, very characteristic, you know, in those times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Unfortunately, looking back to it, we had been taught excessive nationalism, which is no good in its excessiveness.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] those children-- and I was one of them-- who were good material to respond for that sort of exposure, had been given awards, winning the first prize in the-- in the summary.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And all in all, that-- that feeling, that overreaction to that official doctrine has been the cornerstone of a young Hungarian boy's-- Jewish or otherwise-- education.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is very interesting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, of course I have absorbed the religious part of the Jewish component from my grandparents, my motherly grandparents.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when we went for Pesach, when we went for religious occasions, as I said to you earlier, we lived in the detached part of Hungary, which belonged to Czechoslovakia at the time.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to-- had to get a passport every time to go there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was quite a big journey.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we would have-- my mother was very, very strongly attached to her family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we would have gone at least [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] once, twice a year.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
